en_1994869_0	Former President Mahinda Rajapaksa says that he will contest the upcoming general elections.
en_1994869_1	He added that he will come to the forefront to fulfill the needs of the people.
en_1994869_2	The former president expressed these views in Medamulane,  Tangalle on Wednesday July 1.
en_1994869_3	Speaking at the occasion, the former president called on representatives of other political parties to rally around him as they did in 2005.
